{"tid":433592,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《Code Blue》擦愛火　戶田惠梨香傳與細6歲成田凌拍拖","createTime":"2017-10-12T13:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T16:19:05.000Z","uid":3748,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c8579b89e7a0ee1acac3b348338d12320b6458","tid":433592,"uid":3748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"據日媒報導，戶田惠梨香和成田凌今年6月在《Code Blue 3》（港譯：緊急救命3）的製作發布會同場，同月開鏡後關係很快變好，第三次演出該劇的戶田經常給新加入的成田凌不少意見，亦會互相交流演戲心得，情投意合下迅速發展，9月劇集的煞科宴上更整晚坐在一起，狀甚親密，有指由於二人對關係毫不掩飾，戀情隨即在工作人員間傳開，好多電視台人員都知道此事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/210807_a0740797d1c1fca1fb5ff8ab773f5343.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F210807_a0740797d1c1fca1fb5ff8ab773f5343.jpg&h=0b7f884a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/210808_57463fab6ca274383de2d9db71cf247e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F210808_57463fab6ca274383de2d9db71cf247e.jpg&h=f8b27a00&s={SIZE}\" /><strong></strong><br />\n人氣日劇《Code Blue》今夏以第三季回歸締造超高收視，一眾演員新垣結衣、山下智久、新木優子、馬場富美加等人氣一再攀升，雖然劇中感情線無疾而終，無論是「藍白CP」還是「紅白CP」的粉絲都落空收場，沒料到卻誕生了一對意料之外的情侶。消息一傳出即掀起討論，由於在戶田惠梨香和成田凌在劇中對手戲不多，流出交往傳聞令人意外，但普遍網民都送上祝福<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n23歲的成田凌2013年起擔任雜誌《MEN'S NON NO》專屬模特兒，自坂口健太郎今年7月自讓雜誌畢業後成田接手做新任生招牌。成田凌2014年在大熱日劇《逃避雖可恥但有用》中飾演同志角色而為人熟知，去年又有份為新海誠動畫電影《你的名字。》配音，今年接連演出《人100%靠外表》、《Code Blue》等劇，演員之路正值起飛期。不過所謂人紅是非多，他今年初曾傳出跟廣瀨鈴交往，又被爆工作遲大到，難怪粉絲會擔心情路坎坷的戶田惠梨香，今次或又再真心錯付。但也有成田凌粉絲指戶田人氣下滑，外表看起來又有點走樣，同現正人氣急升的小鮮肉不太襯，二人拍拖得益的反而是戶田，對他們之後會怎樣發展也極為關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/210825_ca146e8842b3b6bda2e1bb4a20b4f940.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F210825_ca146e8842b3b6bda2e1bb4a20b4f940.jpg&h=a7e75cc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1c381981af9b497cb24b4c9315d204586e81d75","tid":433592,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:11:09.000Z","msg":"第一張陳小春"},{"pid":"db016abe32d8640189a94b9eb7252e9bb1d0f81b","tid":433592,"uid":3748,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"戶田執到啦<br />\n美男與野獸"},{"pid":"06b46d5b8cb96f38a085e4c8d594846bb12241e2","tid":433592,"uid":3748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:15:59.000Z","msg":"成田凌野剛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7c551325b9d872b238e25a4fc651701ab95e57","tid":433592,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:16:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"515bcba00bd6fa9578c6656c45d5ba0bec83f8cf","tid":433592,"uid":35451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:16:52.000Z","msg":"廚房佬呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞撚左成個s3都冇料到<br />\n食屎啦"},{"pid":"8e75c2a77980427b2b70ace69d357bb48b117b88","tid":433592,"uid":3748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>那個了唷</blockquote><br />\n前前後後n咁多個男友<br />\n咩都玩過哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e314f0f19988115d8fc1a45fd5bcea8b672ad61","tid":433592,"uid":62964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:18:35.000Z","msg":"逃恥14年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3df19656c08a4599201bc501c040dc271dbc35","tid":433592,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戶田執到啦<br />\n美男與野獸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戶田好正囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc0cadcff3a85c20e0de08100b0e628a51acff2","tid":433592,"uid":2